   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">In charger only mode the rectifier is on and charging the
battery. There is no output voltage and the load is not supplied. </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">This mode can for example be used during commissioning to fully
charge the battery before operation. Only a certified and trained
technician may activate charger only mode.</p>
